UPDATE cause SET description = 'Global warming stinks!  Trash does too, but put them together and you\'ve got a winning alternative energy combination.  But how does it work?\r\nHave you ever put your hand in a pile of fertilizer?  It comes out feeling warm and moist (gross!)\r\nFertilizer is a mixture of animal and plant waste products brought together to enrich the soil and help new plants grow.  Fertilizer emits heat as it decomposes, releasing methane, a green house gas that\'s bad for the environment.  But when a power plant burns this trash, capturing and storing the methane that is released, you can create electricity to heat your home or run your computer.\r\nAll this coming from a big pile of trash.  Just think, if we can make electricity from trash what other kinds of alternative power sources could there be?\r\n' WHERE cause_id = 3;

